The paper deals with using publicly available Facebook Pages data to evaluate physical locations for businesses, which involves data analysis and predictive modeling. This suggests that the paper could belong to several sub-categories, including Social and Information Networks (cs.SI), Information Retrieval (cs.IR), Social and Economic Networks (cs.SOC), Databases (cs.DB), and Cybersecurity (cs.CYBER).
